text: Vinz may refer to: ==Persons== *Vinz (singer), part of the duo Nico & Vinz, earlier known as Envy *Ryan Vinz, American video technician *Vinz (rapper), British-Albanian rapper. ==Fiction== *Vinz Clortho, the Keymaster of Gozer, fictional character in the film Ghostbusters ==See also== *Purim Vinz, a Jewish anniversary commemorating the return, in 1616, of the Jews to Frankfurt after a group led by Vincenz Fettmilch organized a pogrom and expelled them out of the city
